      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in exceptional mint condition, and it truly lives up to that designation in every respect. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and all body panels are perfectly aligned with no signs of prior collision or repair work. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim surfaces; all controls, displays, and comfort features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, starting immediately and running with smooth, confident power. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that genuinely feels and performs like it just left the showroom floor \u2014 ideal for a buyer who demands the very best without paying new-car prices.",
      "price": 48500.0,
