      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 as close to showroom-perfect as you'll find on the used market. The exterior is flawless, with no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections of any kind; the finish retains a deep, brilliant shine throughout. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 every surface, seat, and panel looks and feels as though it has barely been touched, with no wear, staining, or odor whatsoever. Under the hood, the engine runs with smooth, responsive power, and all mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and electronics \u2014 perform exactly as intended with zero known issues. Service records are up to date, and the vehicle has been meticulously cared for throughout its life. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic touch-ups, no surprises. Ideal for the discerning buyer who wants the reliability and feel of a new car at a used-car price.",
